Subject: Re: [VB] Jack point repair

Look under the truck and see how the sheet metal looks that attaches to and surrounds the jack
point. Is it badly rusted? If so, you need to repair all this metal before you will be able to
safely use the jack point again. Rust in this area is a common problem.

Steve Bradley
Bradley Auto Body

